title: Hardwell & Jason Derulo - Follow Me [sourced from album]
description:
Hardwell & Jason Derulo - Follow Me [not sure if this is from AciDTox8's copy of the 'United We Are' album though]

Credits to AcidTox8 (I think so at least; other copies have been taken down also which I DL-d some songs from too) for this copy before it had gone off from this site lol XD

Anyways, I never expected a collab between these two. The result? It's an OK enough party song, although I guess it's more worth listening to for Jason Derulo's voice (at least personally); Hardwell sadly didn't make the beat and music as epic as it should, but it's not too bad...
